  "_notes": [
    "Removed from identity[] on 2026-06-05: accounts.google.com,",
    "myaccount.google.com, login.microsoftonline.com, login.live.com.",
    "Reason: these are the consumer auth redirects every Google/Microsoft",
    "service routes through (Gmail, Drive, Outlook, OneDrive, etc.),",
    "so they blocked normal personal-account use by the agent. Apple ID",
    "portal stays because it's rarely hit during normal Mac/iOS use.",
    "Enterprise SSO providers (*.okta.com etc.) stay because they are",
